OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT, DECODE(GFV.NEW_BUSINESSUNITMAP, 64, 'SGPAFA', OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT) TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT, DECODE(GFV.NEW_POSITIONSEQ, NULL, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE2, DECODE(CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE3, NULL, CS_PARTICIPANT.LASTNAME, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE3) GENERICATTRIBUTE3, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE4, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE5, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE6, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE7, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE8, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICBOOLEAN2, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_TXN_DESCRIPTION, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_METHOD, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_AGENT_STATUS, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_NRIC, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_NAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_BENEF_AMOUNT, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_BANKCODE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_BRANCHCODE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNUMBER, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_SETTLMENT_WAY, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_COMPANY_CODE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_INTERM_SWIFTCODE FROM OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL inner join CS_PARTICIPANT CS_PARTICIPANT on CS_PARTICIPANT.PAYEESEQ = OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYEESEQ AND CS_PARTICIPANT.REMOVEDATE > SYSDATE inner join IN_ETL_CONTROL IN_CYCLEDATE OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' AND DECODE(GFV.NEW_BUSINESSUNITMAP, 64, 'SGPAFA', OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT) in ($$STR_BUSINESS_UNIT) AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ NOT IN (SELECT DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ FROM OUT_PAYMENT_RESULT_TRACE WHERE TXT_STATUS = 'ACTIVE') AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY = '$$STR_SGD' AND
